      "translationId": "peshitta",
      "bookSlug": "luke",
      "chapterNumber": 2,
      "verseNumber": 19,
      "referenceLabel": "Luke 2:19",
      "text": "ܡܪܝܡ ܕܝܢ ܢܛܪܐ ܗܘܬ ܟܠܗܝܢ ܡܠܐ ܗܠܝܢ ܘܡܦܚܡܐ ܒܠܒܗ ܀",
      "paragraphStart": false
